## Git Worktrees

Worktrees need setup because `node_modules/` and `dist/` are gitignored.

```bash
# Create worktree (via Claude Code command)
/worktree-add my-feature

# Manual setup (if needed)
cd .worktrees/my-feature
./scripts/setup-worktree.sh
```

The `setup-worktree.sh` script runs `npm install` + `turbo run build` automatically.

