## Maintenance

When adding new apps or packages:
1. Run `bash packages/mcp-ts-engineer/scripts/update.sh`
2. Create codemap: `.claude/codemaps/{project}.md`
3. Add GitHub labels: `bash packages/mcp-ts-engineer/scripts/setup-issue-labels.sh`
4. Create spec directory: `mkdir -p docs/specs/{project}/todo/`

